snippet.title: Journey Escape - Atari 2600 game play
snippet.description: This is Journey Escape for the Atari 2600. This is by far one of the weirdest games that I have for the 2600. Its really odd. Really... You control this guy and the object is collect robots. Yeah, robots.... I wish I started out with $50,000.
